{# "content" was already escaped/paragraph-wrapped by EmailTemplateRenderer::contentToHtml() - trusted HTML at this point, output with |raw.
   "text-left" is required: the site's generic "td{text-align:center}" table rule would otherwise center body text once wrapped
   through EmailLayoutProviderInterface - color/font-family are left to the theme/the _wrapper.html.twig fallback, same as heading.html.twig #}
<tr>
    <td class="text-left" style="padding:0 24px 16px;font-size:15px;line-height:22px;">
        {{ content|raw }}
    </td>
</tr>
